==Other versions of the legendarium==
The first bearer of the name ''Boromir'' in the early versions of the [[legendarium]] was the character later named [[Borlach]].<ref>{{LR|AB}}, note to Annal 263</ref><ref>{{WJ|P1}}, note to §174</ref>

